description: Pan World 100PX Compact Magnetic Drive Water Pump. For OEM and general applications, offering ceramic bearing and ceramic spindle as standard wearing parts to achieve long life expectancy. 792 GPH max flow at 0 head feet. 492 GPH max flow at 13.1 head feet. 3/4 inch MPT threaded inlet and outlet. 20.7 feet maximum head. Motor input is 120 watts. 120 volt Warranty: 2-year full manufacturer warranty on parts and labor.
